2021-22:

Member of 200 yard free relay team that earned Honorable Mention All-American honors for 16th place at the NCAA Championships

Part of 400 yard free relay team that came in 17th in the NCAA Championships

Came in 29th in the 100 yard butterfly at the NCAA Championships

Helped lead Statesmen to fifth straight NSISC Championship title

Part of 200 medley relay that came in second in the 200 yard medley relay at the NSISC Championship

Member of 200 yard free relay to come in second at the NSISC Championships

Finished second with the 800 yard free relay team that the NSISC Championships

2020-21:

Helped lead the Statesmen to fourth straight NSISC Chapmionship title

Finished 12th in the 50 yard free at the NSISC Championship

Came in seventh in the 100 yard butterfly at the NSISC Championship

2019-2020:

Competed as a relay-only swimmer at the NCAA Championships

Member of 400 medley relay team that finished in 11th

Finished 10th in the 50 freestyle at the NSISC Championships

Member of 200 medley relay that won the event

Placed third in the 100 butterfly

Part of the 400 medley relay team that took the NSISC title

Came in third in the 200 butterfly.

Finished 10th in the 100 freestyle

Helped the 400 freestyle relay team to 10th place

Swam at Oak Grove high School for Coach Tammy Evans

Set state record in the 100 yard butterfly

Helped set state record in the 400 free relay

Five time state champion in the 100 yard butterfly

State champion in 100 yard backstroke

Born in Hattiesburg, Miss.

Son of Billy and Teri Miller

Majoring in mathematics
